memberOrga:
EAEVE has 105 members (Veterinary Schools) from 37 countries; 76 members represent Veterinary Schools in the European Union and 29 members represent Veterinary Schools of some other non-EU and non-European countries including Russia, Turkey, Ukraine, Israel, Japan, Jordan and Tunisia. EAEVE members are not natural persons but institutions of higher education (Veterinary Schools) in Europe. Considering a media of 500 staff (academic and support staff) and 1000 students, the population associated to EAEVE would be estimated in 157,500 natural persons.&#xd;
&#xd;
For further information on our members, please consult our website: https://www.eaeve.org/about-eaeve/members.html.
